    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.25.30" />
                <fw type="curatorial">30</fw>
                
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Skyrim, Aug. 24, 59</dateline>
                <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I've just returned from roving in the West with Dr. Lucile and Dr. Bower Aly. We had a wonderful and profitable time looking up places where I've lived. I'll tell you when you arrive, and I'm <hi rend="underline">so happy</hi> you are actually coming on the 28th!</p>
                
                <p>Bless you!</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately,</salute>
                <signed>John N.</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="authorial">Affectionate thoughts for Nita too!</note>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
